body:

The 2025 edition of PyCon DE & PyData took place 23–25 April 2025 at the darmstadtium in Darmstadt. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2025.pycon.de/).
